  2→ * Graph-Reactive Coordination Acceptance Test Kit
  3→ *
  4→ * Extends the shared acceptance-test-kit with reactive coordination helpers.
  5→ * All helpers use business language -- no technical jargon in function names.
  6→ *
  7→ * Driving ports:
  8→ *   GET  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/feed/stream   (SSE feed stream)
  9→ *   GET  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/feed           (initial feed state)
